Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.34,0:01:52.76,OPED_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}不管前方等待的是怎样命运
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.20,0:01:57.16,OPED_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fad(50,50)}そう　高く越えてく
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.20,0:01:57.16,OPED_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}我们定能跨越
